198
00:12:41.053 --> 00:12:41.970
<font color="#fecb00">Manager.</font>

199
00:12:41.971 --> 00:12:43.012
<font color="#fecb00">Asshole.</font>

200
00:12:43.013 --> 00:12:44.640
<font color="#fecb00">[chuckles] Guilty of all charges.</font>

201
00:12:45.849 --> 00:12:47.976
<font color="#fecb00">[in English] Wait.
You have your own bottle?</font>

202
00:12:48.894 --> 00:12:50.478
<font color="#fecb00">You are as pretentious as I thought.</font>

203
00:12:50.479 --> 00:12:51.562
<font color="#fecb00">That's how it works here.</font>

204
00:12:51.563 --> 00:12:52.814
<font color="#fecb00">Uh-huh.</font>

205
00:12:53.732 --> 00:12:56.493
<font color="#fecb00">- [in Japanese] But maybe we can do better.
- [Sota. in English] Okay.</font>

206
00:13:00.113 --> 00:13:01.739
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. Okay.</font>

207
00:13:01.740 --> 00:13:03.241
<font color="#fecb00">So. you're a successful artist.</font>

208
00:13:03.242 --> 00:13:04.367
<font color="#fecb00">I designed the lighting here.</font>

209
00:13:04.368 --> 00:13:05.327
<font color="#fecb00">[glasses clinking]</font>

210
00:13:05.328 --> 00:13:07.453
<font color="#fecb00">- What? No way.
- Yeah.</font>

211
00:13:07.454 --> 00:13:08.372
<font color="#fecb00">Oh.</font>

212
00:13:08.373 --> 00:13:11.083
<font color="#fecb00">So. he lets me pretend.
and even open early for me.</font>

213
00:13:12.376 --> 00:13:13.544
<font color="#fecb00">[speaks Japanese]</font>

214
00:13:19.716 --> 00:13:20.717
<font color="#fecb00">What do you do?</font>

215
00:13:21.218 --> 00:13:22.845
<font color="#fecb00">Uh. computer shit.</font>

216
00:13:23.345 --> 00:13:27.390
<font color="#fecb00">It's not nearly as interesting as art.
How long have you been doing it?</font>

217
00:13:27.391 --> 00:13:28.474
<font color="#fecb00">Since I was little.</font>

218
00:13:28.475 --> 00:13:30.643
<font color="#fecb00">But as a job. I guess. since tonight.</font>

219
00:13:30.644 --> 00:13:33.187
<font color="#fecb00">What? Like-- What do you mean? [chuckles]</font>

220
00:13:33.188 --> 00:13:35.065
<font color="#fecb00">- Like. tonight's your first show?
- Yeah.</font>

221
00:13:36.275 --> 00:13:38.192
<font color="#fecb00">Don't you feel like you should be there?</font>

222
00:13:38.193 --> 00:13:40.237
<font color="#fecb00">Um. I'm letting the suspense build.</font>

223
00:13:40.988 --> 00:13:43.739
<font color="#fecb00">- It's all part of the act.
- Oh. Part of the act.</font>

224
00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:45.074
<font color="#fecb00">Is this part of the act?</font>

225
00:13:45.075 --> 00:13:46.450
<font color="#fecb00">W-What do you mean?</font>

226
00:13:46.451 --> 00:13:50.122
<font color="#fecb00">The secret whiskey bar and you.
the artist. next big thing.</font>

227
00:13:51.540 --> 00:13:53.040
<font color="#fecb00">[in Japanese] Does he bring other girls?</font>

228
00:13:53.041 --> 00:13:55.501
<font color="#fecb00">As a bartender. I can't say.</font>

229
00:13:55.502 --> 00:13:57.378
<font color="#fecb00">- [chuckles]
- [chuckles] Asshole.</font>

230
00:13:57.379 --> 00:13:59.589
<font color="#fecb00">[in English] I mean.
I didn't say it was a bad act.</font>

231
00:13:59.590 --> 00:14:01.091
<font color="#fecb00">I mean. as far as acts go.</font>

232
00:14:03.051 --> 00:14:04.219
<font color="#fecb00">This isn't an act.</font>

233
00:14:06.805 --> 00:14:10.808
<font color="#fecb00">I judge an artist based on their art.
not on a suit and a haircut.</font>

234
00:14:10.809 --> 00:14:12.394
<font color="#fecb00">- [lock clicking]
- [keys jingle]</font>

235
00:14:18.358 --> 00:14:19.443
<font color="#fecb00">[door closes]</font>

236
00:14:24.156 --> 00:14:25.157
<font color="#fecb00">What?</font>

237
00:14:25.657 --> 00:14:27.534
<font color="#fecb00">Why isn't this stuff in the gallery?</font>

238
00:14:28.076 --> 00:14:29.703
<font color="#fecb00">[Kentaro] These aren't for sale.</font>

239
00:14:31.496 --> 00:14:32.497
<font color="#fecb00">[May sighs]</font>

240
00:14:33.248 --> 00:14:35.375
<font color="#fecb00">You're definitely
more than just a haircut.</font>

241
00:14:37.294 --> 00:14:38.712
<font color="#fecb00">Kimi sent me to her stylist.</font>

242
00:14:39.671 --> 00:14:40.964
<font color="#fecb00">People buy the artist.</font>

243
00:14:42.633 --> 00:14:44.718
<font color="#fecb00">I mean. sure.</font>

244
00:14:45.677 --> 00:14:49.056
<font color="#fecb00">Rich pricks who have
more money than good taste.</font>

245
00:14:51.308 --> 00:14:54.144
<font color="#fecb00">Why don't you tell Kimi
what pieces you want in the show?</font>

246
00:14:55.062 --> 00:14:56.063
<font color="#fecb00">[Kentaro] Hmm.</font>

247
00:14:56.939 --> 00:14:57.981
<font color="#fecb00">It's her gallery.</font>

248
00:14:58.815 --> 00:15:01.527
<font color="#fecb00">- She was taking a chance on me--
- Chance on you?</font>

249
00:15:02.945 --> 00:15:04.655
<font color="#fecb00">Like. out of the goodness of her heart?</font>

250
00:15:05.739 --> 00:15:07.199
<font color="#fecb00">Come on. That's bullshit.</font>

251
00:15:07.741 --> 00:15:11.411
<font color="#fecb00">People don't give other people a shot
unless there's something in it for them.</font>

252
00:15:13.413 --> 00:15:14.540
<font color="#fecb00">That's pretty cynical.</font>

253
00:15:16.250 --> 00:15:17.251
<font color="#fecb00">That's life.</font>

254
00:15:18.502 --> 00:15:19.753
<font color="#fecb00">[cell phone chimes]</font>

255
00:15:25.425 --> 00:15:26.676
<font color="#fecb00">You should probably go.</font>

256
00:15:26.677 --> 00:15:29.763
<font color="#fecb00">The. um-- The rich pricks are waiting.</font>

257
00:15:36.270 --> 00:15:37.271
<font color="#fecb00">Come with me.</font>

258
00:15:38.772 --> 00:15:40.147
<font color="#fecb00">Not really my crowd.</font>

259
00:15:40.148 --> 00:15:41.233
<font color="#fecb00">Mine either.</font>

260
00:15:41.733 --> 00:15:43.986
<font color="#fecb00">[chuckles] Get used to it. hotshot.</font>

261
00:15:47.573 --> 00:15:49.241
<font color="#fecb00">Wait. [grunts]</font>

262
00:15:53.662 --> 00:15:54.663
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

263
00:15:55.372 --> 00:15:56.372
<font color="#fecb00">Now you can go.</font>

264
00:15:56.373 --> 00:15:57.833
<font color="#fecb00">- [scoffs]
- [chuckles]</font>

265
00:16:17.227 --> 00:16:18.561
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate sighs] Okay.</font>

266
00:16:18.562 --> 00:16:19.980
<font color="#fecb00">Somebody has to say it.</font>

267
00:16:20.898 --> 00:16:22.232
<font color="#fecb00">I don't see any buildings.</font>

268
00:16:24.318 --> 00:16:25.484
<font color="#fecb00">It must be behind those hills.</font>

269
00:16:25.485 --> 00:16:27.612
<font color="#fecb00">[sighs] Must it?</font>

270
00:16:27.613 --> 00:16:29.822
<font color="#fecb00">- Kentaro. we agreed--
- You all agreed.</font>

271
00:16:29.823 --> 00:16:31.616
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] You got passion. kid.
I'll give you that.</font>

272
00:16:31.617 --> 00:16:34.369
<font color="#fecb00">- Stop treating me like a kid.
- [Cate stammers] Hold on.</font>

273
00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:35.996
<font color="#fecb00">I know what I saw.</font>

274
00:16:35.997 --> 00:16:37.205
<font color="#fecb00">- [Cate] No. no. no.
- [Lee] What?</font>

275
00:16:37.206 --> 00:16:38.290
<font color="#fecb00">Over there.</font>

276
00:16:39.041 --> 00:16:41.334
<font color="#fecb00">- [Lee] What? Where?
- [Cate] Right there. What is that?</font>

277
00:16:41.335 --> 00:16:42.460
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] Oh. yeah. I see it.</font>

278
00:16:42.461 --> 00:16:45.087
<font color="#fecb00">I don't know. Lights on an oil rig maybe.
or a local settlement.</font>

279
00:16:45.088 --> 00:16:47.216
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] Point is. it's out there. right?</font>

280
00:16:48.467 --> 00:16:50.635
<font color="#fecb00">- We follow something we can all see.
- Yeah.</font>

281
00:16:50.636 --> 00:16:51.802
<font color="#fecb00">You don't know how far that is.</font>

282
00:16:51.803 --> 00:16:54.263
<font color="#fecb00">That Titan can catch you
before you get halfway there.</font>

283
00:16:54.264 --> 00:16:55.890
<font color="#fecb00">Whatever I saw is closer.</font>

284
00:16:55.891 --> 00:16:58.644
<font color="#fecb00">- Yeah. if it exists.
- [May] Okay. Kentaro.</font>

285
00:16:59.895 --> 00:17:04.191
<font color="#fecb00">Look. you have a brilliant imagination.
but now is not the time to use it.</font>

286
00:17:05.776 --> 00:17:06.776
<font color="#fecb00">I'm going.</font>

287
00:17:08.529 --> 00:17:09.862
<font color="#fecb00">Alone if I have to.</font>

288
00:17:09.863 --> 00:17:12.657
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God. You obstinate asshole.</font>

289
00:17:13.909 --> 00:17:16.285
<font color="#fecb00">- So. what? You wanna die to prove a point?
- Do you?</font>

290
00:17:16.286 --> 00:17:18.454
<font color="#fecb00">- No.
- [Lee] Stop. Stop. Please. stop.</font>

291
00:17:20.123 --> 00:17:21.249
<font color="#fecb00">You think you saw something?</font>

292
00:17:21.250 --> 00:17:22.375
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. I know what I saw.</font>

293
00:17:22.376 --> 00:17:26.420
<font color="#fecb00">Then go. and don't stop until you find it.
and then get help.</font>

294
00:17:26.421 --> 00:17:27.506
<font color="#fecb00">We'll do the same.</font>

295
00:17:29.299 --> 00:17:30.299
<font color="#fecb00">Good luck.</font>

296
00:17:30.300 --> 00:17:31.844
<font color="#fecb00">We're all gonna need it.</font>

297
00:17:38.225 --> 00:17:40.560
<font color="#fecb00">No. No. We can't just let him leave.</font>

298
00:17:40.561 --> 00:17:42.855
<font color="#fecb00">He's made his choice. Cate. Let's go.</font>

299
00:17:55.450 --> 00:17:58.494
<font color="#fecb00">[Verdugo] Dr. Barnes. I understand
you have something for us?</font>

300
00:17:58.495 --> 00:18:00.663
<font color="#fecb00">[Barnes] Yeah. Hold on.
Sharing my screen now.</font>

301
00:18:00.664 --> 00:18:02.290
<font color="#fecb00">- What are we looking at here?
- Radiation.</font>

302
00:18:02.291 --> 00:18:04.375
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Specifically. gamma rays
in the 30 exahertz range.</i></font>

303
00:18:04.376 --> 00:18:07.044
<font color="#fecb00">- Where is this radiation coming from?
- That's the crazy thing.</font>

304
00:18:07.045 --> 00:18:09.297
<font color="#fecb00"><i>You only see these kinds
of spikes from pulsars.</i></font>

305
00:18:09.298 --> 00:18:12.300
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Supermassive black holes from outer space.</i></font>

306
00:18:12.301 --> 00:18:13.634
<font color="#fecb00">- But not this?
- No.</font>

307
00:18:13.635 --> 00:18:15.094
<font color="#fecb00"><i>This was coming from the earth.</i></font>

308
00:18:15.095 --> 00:18:16.304
<font color="#fecb00">Where exactly on the earth?</font>

309
00:18:16.305 --> 00:18:18.931
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Well. the detector that picked it up
is an old model.</i></font>

310
00:18:18.932 --> 00:18:20.016
<font color="#fecb00"><i>it's pretty much an antique.</i></font>

311
00:18:20.017 --> 00:18:22.018
<font color="#fecb00">- They're pretty finicky.
- I'll note it in the next budget request.</font>

312
00:18:22.019 --> 00:18:23.769
<font color="#fecb00">- Where?
- It was a rhythmic pulse.</font>

313
00:18:23.770 --> 00:18:25.521
<font color="#fecb00"><i>well. like-- like a pulsar</i></font>

314
00:18:25.522 --> 00:18:28.609
<font color="#fecb00"><i>but as far as I know.
there aren't any pulsars in Alaska.</i></font>

315
00:18:30.110 --> 00:18:32.111
<font color="#fecb00">Thank you. Dr. Barnes.
Send us everything you have</font>

316
00:18:32.112 --> 00:18:34.363
<font color="#fecb00">and we'll get an analysis team
out to you right away.</font>

317
00:18:34.364 --> 00:18:36.240
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Wait. wait. wait!
That's not the big thing.</i></font>

318
00:18:36.241 --> 00:18:38.409
<font color="#fecb00"><i>The last time anyone
saw readings like this</i></font>

319
00:18:38.410 --> 00:18:40.537
<font color="#fecb00"><i>was right before the last emergence event.</i></font>

320
00:18:41.121 --> 00:18:42.955
<font color="#fecb00"><i>From Janjira and Yucca Flats.</i></font>

321
00:18:42.956 --> 00:18:44.416
<font color="#fecb00">Before G-Day.</font>

322
00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:58.764
<font color="#fecb00">[breathing heavily]</font>

323
00:18:59.932 --> 00:19:01.974
<font color="#fecb00">[May. echoing] Kentaro!</font>

324
00:19:01.975 --> 00:19:03.310
<font color="#fecb00">[Kentaro] May?</font>

325
00:19:03.894 --> 00:19:04.895
<font color="#fecb00">Is that you?</font>

326
00:19:05.979 --> 00:19:07.688
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate. echoing] Kentaro!</font>

327
00:19:07.689 --> 00:19:08.857
<font color="#fecb00">Cate?</font>

328
00:19:09.650 --> 00:19:10.651
<font color="#fecb00">Shaw?</font>

329
00:19:11.902 --> 00:19:14.238
<font color="#fecb00">[voices whispering]</font>

330
00:19:35.717 --> 00:19:38.177
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] We shouldn't have let Kentaro go.</font>

331
00:19:38.178 --> 00:19:39.971
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts] He won't survive the night.</font>

332
00:19:39.972 --> 00:19:41.055
<font color="#fecb00">[sighs]</font>

333
00:19:41.056 --> 00:19:42.765
<font color="#fecb00">He just needs to hang on
until we get help.</font>

334
00:19:42.766 --> 00:19:44.977
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts. breathing heavily]</font>

335
00:19:46.562 --> 00:19:49.981
<font color="#fecb00">- Come on. May. let me carry that bag.
- No. Stop. No!</font>

336
00:19:49.982 --> 00:19:51.066
<font color="#fecb00">He wants something.</font>

337
00:19:51.984 --> 00:19:53.193
<font color="#fecb00">She's getting delirious.</font>

338
00:19:55.654 --> 00:19:57.823
<font color="#fecb00">Few more steps. okay?</font>

339
00:19:58.657 --> 00:20:01.118
<font color="#fecb00">Think of how warm it'll be
when we get there.</font>

340
00:20:02.703 --> 00:20:05.122
<font color="#fecb00">Blankets. hot coffee.</font>

341
00:20:06.039 --> 00:20:07.623
<font color="#fecb00">- Whiskey.
- [chuckles]</font>

342
00:20:07.624 --> 00:20:09.334
<font color="#fecb00">[breathing heavily] Come on.</font>

343
00:20:29.229 --> 00:20:30.480
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts]</font>

344
00:20:32.191 --> 00:20:33.192
<font color="#fecb00">No.</font>

345
00:20:44.703 --> 00:20:46.955
<font color="#fecb00">[all grunting]</font>

346
00:20:49.666 --> 00:20:52.336
<font color="#fecb00">[breathing heavily. groans] Shit.</font>

347
00:20:53.003 --> 00:20:55.881
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] What? We're back at Dad's tent?</font>

348
00:20:58.467 --> 00:21:00.218
<font color="#fecb00">- How did this happen?
- [sighs]</font>

349
00:21:00.219 --> 00:21:01.636
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] We're walking in circles.</font>

350
00:21:01.637 --> 00:21:05.598
<font color="#fecb00">Uh. Titans have odd effects
on their surroundings</font>

351
00:21:05.599 --> 00:21:07.600
<font color="#fecb00">and how we experience them.</font>

352
00:21:07.601 --> 00:21:12.105
<font color="#fecb00">The cloud we flew through. this place.
it's stranger than you think.</font>

353
00:21:12.940 --> 00:21:14.858
<font color="#fecb00">It's stranger than anybody knows.</font>

354
00:21:16.235 --> 00:21:18.153
<font color="#fecb00">[shivering]</font>

355
00:21:21.615 --> 00:21:23.866
<font color="#fecb00">If we don't warm her up. she's gonna die.</font>

356
00:21:23.867 --> 00:21:26.410
<font color="#fecb00">We can all die if that Titan's still here.</font>

357
00:21:26.411 --> 00:21:28.288
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I'm not leaving here without her.</font>

358
00:21:29.206 --> 00:21:30.874
<font color="#fecb00">We are not losing another person.</font>

359
00:21:49.142 --> 00:21:50.143
<font color="#fecb00">Beautiful.</font>

360
00:22:02.155 --> 00:22:03.156
<font color="#fecb00">It is.</font>

361
00:22:07.786 --> 00:22:10.956
<font color="#fecb00">Tell me why you don't wanna go
to your gallery opening again.</font>

362
00:22:14.918 --> 00:22:16.670
<font color="#fecb00">Why does it matter to you if I go?</font>

363
00:22:18.630 --> 00:22:19.714
<font color="#fecb00">Well. it doesn't.</font>

364
00:22:19.715 --> 00:22:23.927
<font color="#fecb00">But I don't think you should be ashamed
to take credit for what you do.</font>

365
00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:25.721
<font color="#fecb00">What do you do?</font>

366
00:22:30.058 --> 00:22:32.811
<font color="#fecb00">I just brought you here
and bared my artist's soul.</font>

367
00:22:33.812 --> 00:22:35.855
<font color="#fecb00">You haven't told me shit about yourself.</font>

368
00:22:35.856 --> 00:22:38.274
<font color="#fecb00">I told you. I do computer shit.</font>

369
00:22:38.275 --> 00:22:39.734
<font color="#fecb00">- Computer shit?
- Yeah.</font>

370
00:22:39.735 --> 00:22:40.819
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. okay. Come on.</font>

371
00:22:53.999 --> 00:22:58.337
<font color="#fecb00">I'm from Tacoma. Tacoma sucks.
So. I came to Japan.</font>

372
00:22:59.213 --> 00:23:00.631
<font color="#fecb00">Japan is cool.</font>

373
00:23:01.507 --> 00:23:02.507
<font color="#fecb00">Is that better?</font>

374
00:23:03.133 --> 00:23:04.333
<font color="#fecb00">[Kentaro muttering] I'm sorry.</font>

375
00:23:04.635 --> 00:23:06.887
<font color="#fecb00">It's okay. You didn't make Tacoma suck.</font>

376
00:23:11.308 --> 00:23:14.519
<font color="#fecb00">So. you can stay as long as you want.
or you can come with me?</font>

377
00:23:14.520 --> 00:23:16.771
<font color="#fecb00">This is your party. [sighs]</font>

378
00:23:16.772 --> 00:23:18.732
<font color="#fecb00">I've already seen all the best stuff.</font>

379
00:23:19.483 --> 00:23:20.817
<font color="#fecb00">Can I see you again?</font>

380
00:23:26.990 --> 00:23:29.033
<font color="#fecb00">- Give me your number. [chuckles]
- This is your phone?</font>

381
00:23:29.034 --> 00:23:30.702
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. I like a physical button.</font>

382
00:23:34.164 --> 00:23:36.291
<font color="#fecb00">- [cell phone ringing]
- [Kentaro] Um. you need to--</font>

383
00:23:37.125 --> 00:23:38.167
<font color="#fecb00">Ignore it.</font>

384
00:23:38.168 --> 00:23:39.628
<font color="#fecb00">[buttons beeping]</font>

385
00:23:40.838 --> 00:23:42.171
<font color="#fecb00">Try not to break anything.</font>

386
00:23:42.172 --> 00:23:44.132
<font color="#fecb00">[chuckles] How would you tell?</font>

387
00:23:45.425 --> 00:23:46.927
<font color="#fecb00">[cell phone ringing]</font>

388
00:23:56.228 --> 00:23:57.688
<font color="#fecb00">Hello? Hey.</font>

389
00:23:58.272 --> 00:24:00.315
<font color="#fecb00">[sighs] I'm traveling.</font>

390
00:24:01.441 --> 00:24:02.442
<font color="#fecb00">For work. yeah.</font>

391
00:24:05.362 --> 00:24:08.073
<font color="#fecb00">No. Look. you-- you gotta stop calling me.</font>

392
00:24:08.574 --> 00:24:12.911
<font color="#fecb00">I-- [sighs] I'll call you
when I'm back. yeah?</font>

393
00:24:14.955 --> 00:24:15.956
<font color="#fecb00">Okay. you too.</font>

394
00:24:17.082 --> 00:24:18.083
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. bye.</font>

395
00:24:41.106 --> 00:24:42.107
<font color="#fecb00">Beautiful.</font>

396
00:24:44.651 --> 00:24:46.903
<font color="#fecb00">Beautiful. [shivering]</font>

397
00:24:46.904 --> 00:24:49.489
<font color="#fecb00">- This shit is so beautiful.
- [Cate] May.</font>

398
00:24:50.991 --> 00:24:53.284
<font color="#fecb00">Stay with me. May. May.</font>

399
00:24:53.285 --> 00:24:56.330
<font color="#fecb00">Oh-- [stammers] My legs are burning.</font>

400
00:24:57.039 --> 00:24:58.414
<font color="#fecb00">Like pins and needles?</font>

401
00:24:58.415 --> 00:25:00.374
<font color="#fecb00">More like swords and daggers.</font>

402
00:25:00.375 --> 00:25:02.211
<font color="#fecb00">- [groans]
- That's really good.</font>

403
00:25:03.170 --> 00:25:04.629
<font color="#fecb00">Your nerves are waking up.</font>

404
00:25:04.630 --> 00:25:06.005
<font color="#fecb00">You don't have frostbite yet.</font>

405
00:25:06.006 --> 00:25:07.715
<font color="#fecb00">[May breathes shakily] Yet.</font>

406
00:25:07.716 --> 00:25:09.091
<font color="#fecb00">Good bedside manner.</font>

407
00:25:09.092 --> 00:25:10.719
<font color="#fecb00">[shivering]</font>

408
00:25:12.095 --> 00:25:17.892
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. If anything happens to me.
just get in touch with my sister.</font>

409
00:25:17.893 --> 00:25:20.394
<font color="#fecb00">Her name's-- [inhales sharply]
Her name is Lyra.</font>

410
00:25:20.395 --> 00:25:21.688
<font color="#fecb00">No. Let's not go there.</font>

411
00:25:22.940 --> 00:25:25.943
<font color="#fecb00">She's the only--
only person that I can call.</font>

412
00:25:27.110 --> 00:25:30.029
<font color="#fecb00">I'm gonna-- I'm gonna give you her number.</font>

413
00:25:30.030 --> 00:25:31.155
<font color="#fecb00">I'm sure Kentaro knows h--</font>

414
00:25:31.156 --> 00:25:33.950
<font color="#fecb00">No. He doesn't know shit.</font>

415
00:25:33.951 --> 00:25:36.161
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] Hope you're not talking about me.</font>

416
00:25:36.995 --> 00:25:39.039
<font color="#fecb00">[sighs] Compliments of Du-Ho.</font>

417
00:25:40.415 --> 00:25:41.708
<font color="#fecb00">Crackers and chocolate.</font>

418
00:25:42.709 --> 00:25:43.918
<font color="#fecb00">How's she doing?</font>

419
00:25:43.919 --> 00:25:45.379
<font color="#fecb00">[breathes shakily] Better.</font>

420
00:25:52.219 --> 00:25:53.303
<font color="#fecb00">[exhales sharply]</font>

421
00:25:54.555 --> 00:25:56.807
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] All right. Her pants are dry.</font>

422
00:26:01.019 --> 00:26:03.062
<font color="#fecb00">[groans] We're gonna
have to stoke that fire.</font>

423
00:26:03.063 --> 00:26:04.272
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts]</font>

424
00:26:04.273 --> 00:26:07.568
<font color="#fecb00">This is nothing but kindling.
I mean. it's not gonna last very long.</font>

425
00:26:09.862 --> 00:26:11.697
<font color="#fecb00">And who knows what's in your dad's papers.</font>

426
00:26:12.364 --> 00:26:15.367
<font color="#fecb00">I mean. it could tell us
what he was doing here.</font>

427
00:26:16.493 --> 00:26:19.329
<font color="#fecb00">Theories. discoveries. where he went.</font>

428
00:26:20.247 --> 00:26:21.957
<font color="#fecb00">[shivering]</font>

429
00:26:25.002 --> 00:26:26.170
<font color="#fecb00">Let it burn.</font>

430
00:26:26.962 --> 00:26:27.963
<font color="#fecb00">[breathing deeply]</font>

431
00:26:40.517 --> 00:26:41.810
<font color="#fecb00">[rumbling]</font>

432
00:26:45.022 --> 00:26:47.857
<font color="#fecb00">Get your gear on! We gotta move! Come on!</font>

433
00:26:47.858 --> 00:26:49.275
<font color="#fecb00">Get back to where we hid before.</font>

434
00:26:49.276 --> 00:26:50.444
<font color="#fecb00">- Come on.
- May!</font>

435
00:26:51.778 --> 00:26:54.156
<font color="#fecb00">- [whimpers]
- Go. go. go. go. go!</font>

436
00:26:56.158 --> 00:26:58.318
<font color="#fecb00">- [whimpers] May.
- [Lee] Wait. wait. Stop. Don't move.</font>

437
00:26:59.244 --> 00:27:01.205
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] It could be anywhere. Listen.</font>

438
00:27:04.208 --> 00:27:05.292
<font color="#fecb00">[shrieks. gasps]</font>

439
00:27:05.792 --> 00:27:07.836
<font color="#fecb00">[creature roars]</font>

440
00:27:16.887 --> 00:27:18.680
<font color="#fecb00">I can't run from that thing anymore.</font>

441
00:27:23.018 --> 00:27:24.228
<font color="#fecb00">We may not have to.</font>

442
00:27:24.728 --> 00:27:28.523
<font color="#fecb00">This morning.
Outpost 47 registered readings</font>

443
00:27:28.524 --> 00:27:31.610
<font color="#fecb00">I consider noteworthy.</font>

444
00:27:32.819 --> 00:27:33.862
<font color="#fecb00">Dr. Barnes.</font>

445
00:27:34.363 --> 00:27:35.821
<font color="#fecb00">- [tech 1] Oh. my God.
- [tech 2] What?</font>

446
00:27:35.822 --> 00:27:38.699
<font color="#fecb00">That can't be right.
These readings mirror. uh--</font>

447
00:27:38.700 --> 00:27:41.119
<font color="#fecb00">The gamma-ray flare
before the San Francisco...</font>

448
00:27:42.663 --> 00:27:43.664
<font color="#fecb00">event.</font>

449
00:27:44.331 --> 00:27:46.541
<font color="#fecb00">Call it what it was. An attack.</font>

450
00:27:46.542 --> 00:27:48.876
<font color="#fecb00">Well. what do you suggest?
Full mobilization?</font>

451
00:27:48.877 --> 00:27:51.254
<font color="#fecb00">- Try out your Titan warning system?
- [Tim] Uh. excuse me. [clears throat]</font>

452
00:27:51.255 --> 00:27:53.673
<font color="#fecb00">- [Bagheri] Create a worldwide panic?
- Better than a thousand dead.</font>

453
00:27:53.674 --> 00:27:55.466
<font color="#fecb00">- Or 10.000.
- Excuse me.</font>

454
00:27:55.467 --> 00:27:57.802
<font color="#fecb00">[Bagheri] We don't know if these creatures
have malevolent intent.</font>

455
00:27:57.803 --> 00:28:00.055
<font color="#fecb00">- [Tim] Excuse me!
- Quiet down.</font>

456
00:28:01.431 --> 00:28:03.933
<font color="#fecb00">[shushes] Tim. you have something?</font>

457
00:28:03.934 --> 00:28:07.061
<font color="#fecb00"><i>We can't dismiss Bill Randa's files.</i></font>

458
00:28:07.062 --> 00:28:10.356
<font color="#fecb00">Now. look. Lee Shaw was there.
He knows something that we don't.</font>

459
00:28:10.357 --> 00:28:12.818
<font color="#fecb00">- That's why he's going after the files.
- Quiet!</font>

460
00:28:14.069 --> 00:28:17.363
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Uh. most of you all don't know me.
and if you do.</i></font>

461
00:28:17.364 --> 00:28:21.869
<font color="#fecb00"><i>I'm the troll from the basement
that you try to avoid in the break room.</i></font>

462
00:28:22.578 --> 00:28:25.496
<font color="#fecb00">It's fine. It's not like I work here
for the after-work karaoke anyway.</font>

463
00:28:25.497 --> 00:28:26.707
<font color="#fecb00">Your point.</font>

464
00:28:27.207 --> 00:28:30.919
<font color="#fecb00">[sighs] I thought that we were here</font>

465
00:28:31.503 --> 00:28:35.382
<font color="#fecb00"><i>to learn everything we can
in any way that we can</i></font>

466
00:28:35.883 --> 00:28:39.428
<font color="#fecb00"><i>so no one else has to lose
another loved one in a Titan event.</i></font>

467
00:28:39.928 --> 00:28:42.555
<font color="#fecb00"><i>And I would've thought
that a bunch of people</i></font>

468
00:28:42.556 --> 00:28:47.436
<font color="#fecb00"><i>who signed up to study
giant. atomic-powered monsters</i></font>

469
00:28:47.936 --> 00:28:49.816
<font color="#fecb00"><i>would be a little bit more
open-minded about it.</i></font>

470
00:28:52.816 --> 00:28:56.236
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] We may be knocked on our asses
but we're not done yet.</font>

471
00:28:56.737 --> 00:28:58.780
<font color="#fecb00">'cause now we know how our enemy works.</font>

472
00:28:59.489 --> 00:29:00.649
<font color="#fecb00">- We do?
- [Shaw groans] Yeah.</font>

473
00:29:01.116 --> 00:29:03.285
<font color="#fecb00">That Titan didn't go after us.
it went after the fire.</font>

474
00:29:03.994 --> 00:29:07.497
<font color="#fecb00">Didn't go after Kentaro. it went after
that burning airplane engine.</font>

475
00:29:09.082 --> 00:29:10.501
<font color="#fecb00">That's how it's tracking us.</font>

476
00:29:11.043 --> 00:29:12.877
<font color="#fecb00">It's drawn to the heat. Oh. my God.</font>

477
00:29:12.878 --> 00:29:16.547
<font color="#fecb00">Then why did it toss that airplane
like a chew toy... [pants]</font>

478
00:29:16.548 --> 00:29:18.133
<font color="#fecb00">...and come chasing after us?</font>

479
00:29:18.884 --> 00:29:22.094
<font color="#fecb00">Because my brother tried saving our asses
by shooting a flare at it.</font>

480
00:29:22.095 --> 00:29:24.556
<font color="#fecb00">And after the flare.
we were the warmest things.</font>

481
00:29:26.892 --> 00:29:30.479
<font color="#fecb00">And this is how we beat this damn thing.</font>

482
00:29:31.146 --> 00:29:34.857
<font color="#fecb00">We dangle the biggest. brightest.
hottest object we can in front of it.</font>

483
00:29:34.858 --> 00:29:37.109
<font color="#fecb00">Never been so thankful for a full bladder.</font>

484
00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:39.153
<font color="#fecb00">Aviation fuel.</font>

485
00:29:39.154 --> 00:29:40.238
<font color="#fecb00">Flint.</font>

486
00:29:40.239 --> 00:29:43.699
<font color="#fecb00">Gonna light this thing brighter
than Times Square on VJ Day.</font>

487
00:29:43.700 --> 00:29:45.076
<font color="#fecb00">Uh. what? What day?</font>

488
00:29:45.077 --> 00:29:47.412
<font color="#fecb00">We build a bonfire. We feed it.</font>

489
00:29:48.413 --> 00:29:50.831
<font color="#fecb00">And then while that Titan's
absorbing its heat...</font>

490
00:29:50.832 --> 00:29:54.753
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts] ...we hightail it to the coast.
I'll carry you if I have to.</font>

491
00:29:55.921 --> 00:29:57.714
<font color="#fecb00">[grunting]</font>

492
00:30:15.774 --> 00:30:17.776
<font color="#fecb00">May. just a little further. okay?</font>

493
00:30:18.569 --> 00:30:19.569
<font color="#fecb00">We're gonna make it.</font>

494
00:30:22.030 --> 00:30:23.156
<font color="#fecb00">I'm not.</font>

495
00:30:24.741 --> 00:30:28.787
<font color="#fecb00">Sooner or later
you're gonna have to ditch me. okay?</font>

496
00:30:30.873 --> 00:30:32.791
<font color="#fecb00">Yes. And if the time comes.</font>

497
00:30:33.834 --> 00:30:35.335
<font color="#fecb00">you ditch him too.</font>

498
00:30:36.712 --> 00:30:38.380
<font color="#fecb00">Save yourself. Cate.</font>

499
00:30:39.173 --> 00:30:41.592
<font color="#fecb00">One of us
has to make it out of here alive.</font>

500
00:30:55.230 --> 00:30:56.398
<font color="#fecb00">[voice. echoing] Who's there?</font>

501
00:31:00.694 --> 00:31:01.695
<font color="#fecb00">Hello?</font>

502
00:31:07.701 --> 00:31:09.995
<font color="#fecb00">- Hello?
- [voice. echoing] What are you doing here?</font>

503
00:31:11.038 --> 00:31:12.206
<font color="#fecb00">Are you real?</font>

504
00:31:13.624 --> 00:31:15.417
<font color="#fecb00">[voice. echoing] I thought I was alone.</font>

505
00:31:16.460 --> 00:31:17.502
<font color="#fecb00">So did I.</font>

506
00:31:17.503 --> 00:31:19.063
<font color="#fecb00">[voice. echoing] You shouldn't be here.</font>

507
00:31:26.929 --> 00:31:28.305
<font color="#fecb00">[in Japanese] Dad...</font>

508
00:31:33.852 --> 00:31:34.978
<font color="#fecb00">Don't leave me!</font>

509
00:31:35.938 --> 00:31:37.189
<font color="#fecb00">Wait. Dad!</font>

510
00:31:37.898 --> 00:31:38.899
<font color="#fecb00">It's me!</font>

511
00:31:40.359 --> 00:31:41.360
<font color="#fecb00">Don't...</font>

512
00:32:10.389 --> 00:32:12.391
<font color="#fecb00">[wheezing. coughing]</font>

513
00:32:39.543 --> 00:32:40.544
<font color="#fecb00">[breathes shakily]</font>

514
00:33:43.398 --> 00:33:44.482
<font color="#fecb00">[scratching]</font>

515
00:33:44.483 --> 00:33:45.817
<font color="#fecb00">[gasps]</font>

516
00:33:55.327 --> 00:33:56.369
<font color="#fecb00">[gasps]</font>

517
00:33:56.370 --> 00:33:57.913
<font color="#fecb00">I did sell a few pieces...</font>

518
00:34:01.291 --> 00:34:03.292
<font color="#fecb00">...but Kimi dropped me anyway.</font>

519
00:34:03.293 --> 00:34:04.628
<font color="#fecb00">[scratching]</font>

520
00:34:08.841 --> 00:34:11.051
<font color="#fecb00">"It's a huge opportunity." you said.</font>

521
00:34:13.762 --> 00:34:15.097
<font color="#fecb00">"You're so talented."</font>

522
00:34:16.181 --> 00:34:17.391
<font color="#fecb00">"You can do this."</font>

523
00:34:18.225 --> 00:34:20.018
<font color="#fecb00">"I believe in you."</font>

524
00:34:20.561 --> 00:34:22.771
<font color="#fecb00">That's what you said that time.</font>

525
00:34:26.440 --> 00:34:27.440
<font color="#fecb00">How the hell...</font>

526
00:34:28.150 --> 00:34:29.862
<font color="#fecb00">...would you know
if I was ready or not?</font>

527
00:34:30.571 --> 00:34:32.989
<font color="#fecb00">But I didn't want to disappoint you.</font>

528
00:34:33.739 --> 00:34:35.534
<font color="#fecb00">So I couldn't face you...</font>

529
00:34:38.745 --> 00:34:41.748
<font color="#fecb00">How was I supposed to know
I'd never see you again?</font>

530
00:34:42.416 --> 00:34:43.625
<font color="#fecb00">Dad?</font>

531
00:34:48.589 --> 00:34:51.925
<font color="#fecb00">I wouldn't have missed this for anything.</font>

532
00:34:52.551 --> 00:34:54.052
<font color="#fecb00">Everybody loved it.</font>

533
00:34:54.803 --> 00:34:56.262
<font color="#fecb00">Your mother loved it.</font>

534
00:34:56.263 --> 00:34:57.639
<font color="#fecb00">[distorted] I loved it too.</font>

535
00:34:58.682 --> 00:34:59.933
<font color="#fecb00">I'm proud of you.</font>

536
00:35:01.727 --> 00:35:02.728
<font color="#fecb00">Congratulations.</font>

537
00:35:03.729 --> 00:35:05.272
<font color="#fecb00">[distorted dialogue]</font>

538
00:35:06.023 --> 00:35:08.025
<font color="#fecb00">[static]</font>

539
00:35:49.399 --> 00:35:50.901
<font color="#fecb00">[static continues]</font>

540
00:35:56.657 --> 00:35:58.408
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate. in English]
Are we really doing this?</font>

541
00:35:58.909 --> 00:36:00.577
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] It's a funeral pyre. Cate.</font>

542
00:36:01.203 --> 00:36:03.955
<font color="#fecb00">Du-Ho always wanted to go out
in a blaze of glory.</font>

543
00:36:03.956 --> 00:36:08.418
<font color="#fecb00">I'm just pouring one out for the guy
who loved getting one over on me.</font>

544
00:36:08.961 --> 00:36:12.797
<font color="#fecb00">First night we met. brother.
I-- I couldn't believe</font>

545
00:36:12.798 --> 00:36:16.050
<font color="#fecb00">how you were drinking me
underneath the table that night.</font>

546
00:36:16.051 --> 00:36:18.553
<font color="#fecb00">- [helicopter whirring]
- [Lee] And then I realized</font>

547
00:36:18.554 --> 00:36:20.930
<font color="#fecb00">- every time you took a shot...
- Do you hear that?</font>

548
00:36:20.931 --> 00:36:22.571
<font color="#fecb00">- Shaw. Shaw! It's--
- ...all you really--</font>

549
00:36:23.433 --> 00:36:25.102
<font color="#fecb00">[roars]</font>

550
00:36:26.353 --> 00:36:28.021
<font color="#fecb00">[both screaming]</font>

551
00:36:30.107 --> 00:36:32.609
<font color="#fecb00">- Go! Run!
- May!</font>

552
00:36:34.820 --> 00:36:37.281
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. big boy! Big boy! Over here!</font>

553
00:36:38.782 --> 00:36:41.243
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. Jesus. No. Where is it? No.</font>

554
00:36:44.580 --> 00:36:46.915
<font color="#fecb00">- Help! Help! Help!
- [grunting]</font>

555
00:36:48.333 --> 00:36:49.835
<font color="#fecb00">- [whimpering]
- [growling]</font>

556
00:36:51.044 --> 00:36:52.462
<font color="#fecb00">[screaming]</font>

557
00:36:54.131 --> 00:36:56.966
<font color="#fecb00">[groans] Need a shield
to ride a rocket ship.</font>

558
00:36:56.967 --> 00:36:59.595
<font color="#fecb00">Dinner time. you son of a bitch. [grunts]</font>

559
00:37:02.222 --> 00:37:03.307
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts]</font>

560
00:37:08.145 --> 00:37:09.813
<font color="#fecb00">[screaming]</font>

561
00:37:11.523 --> 00:37:12.523
<font color="#fecb00">May. come on.</font>

562
00:37:12.524 --> 00:37:13.734
<font color="#fecb00">You can do this.</font>

563
00:37:15.319 --> 00:37:16.403
<font color="#fecb00">The chopper! Let's go.</font>

564
00:37:25.412 --> 00:37:26.663
<font color="#fecb00">[grunting]</font>

565
00:37:31.376 --> 00:37:33.336
<font color="#fecb00">[footsteps thudding]</font>

566
00:37:33.337 --> 00:37:34.546
<font color="#fecb00">[roars]</font>

567
00:37:49.228 --> 00:37:51.605
<font color="#fecb00">- [Cate grunting] May! Come on!
- [May] Oh. shit.</font>

568
00:37:52.689 --> 00:37:53.815
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate] I got you!</font>

569
00:37:55.400 --> 00:37:56.567
<font color="#fecb00">- Come on. hurry!
- [Cate] Kentaro!</font>

570
00:37:56.568 --> 00:37:57.985
<font color="#fecb00">- Let's go!
- Kentaro?</font>

571
00:37:57.986 --> 00:38:00.072
<font color="#fecb00">- [Kentaro] Come on. Go.
- [Lee] Go. Go.</font>

572
00:38:02.157 --> 00:38:03.283
<font color="#fecb00">[Lee] Pick it up!</font>

573
00:38:05.369 --> 00:38:07.203
<font color="#fecb00">[Cate shrieks]</font>

574
00:38:07.204 --> 00:38:08.539
<font color="#fecb00">[grunts]</font>

575
00:38:35.065 --> 00:38:36.399
<font color="#fecb00">They said the signal was so weak.</font>

576
00:38:36.400 --> 00:38:38.902
<font color="#fecb00">they almost didn't hear me
on the emergency channel.</font>

577
00:38:41.196 --> 00:38:44.198
<font color="#fecb00">I never thought I'd thank someone
for abandoning their family.</font>

578
00:38:44.199 --> 00:38:45.784
<font color="#fecb00">but here we are.</font>

579
00:38:47.160 --> 00:38:49.162
<font color="#fecb00">Dad was there. Before me.</font>

580
00:38:50.080 --> 00:38:52.206
<font color="#fecb00">- Just like at his camp.
- How do you--</font>

581
00:38:52.207 --> 00:38:54.584
<font color="#fecb00">Someone had to fix the radio that I found.</font>

582
00:38:54.585 --> 00:38:56.253
<font color="#fecb00">Left a mess of shavings behind.</font>

583
00:39:00.048 --> 00:39:01.382
<font color="#fecb00">He made it out.</font>

584
00:39:01.383 --> 00:39:02.634
<font color="#fecb00">He's alive.</font>

585
00:39:03.760 --> 00:39:05.137
<font color="#fecb00">[May] Thank you.</font>

586
00:39:20.694 --> 00:39:22.446
<font color="#fecb00">[radio chatter]</font>

587
00:39:24.948 --> 00:39:29.912
<font color="#fecb00">No. No. no. no. Oh. goddamn it.</font>

588
00:39:30.579 --> 00:39:31.580
<font color="#fecb00">Damn it.</font>

589
00:39:42.716 --> 00:39:43.884
<font color="#fecb00">[Tim] Colonel Shaw!</font>

590
00:39:45.511 --> 00:39:47.262
<font color="#fecb00">It's an honor to finally meet you!</font>

